<!-- ====== FAQ ====== -->
<section class="th-faq">
  <div class="th-faq__container">
    <h2 class="th-faq__heading fade-in">Common questions</h2>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">What can you help me with?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">We focus on the three big Malassezia conditions: fungal acne, seborrheic dermatitis, and tinea versicolor. They're all driven by the same yeast, but each one needs its own approach. Our providers know the difference and treat them accordingly.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">What happens during a consultation?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">You'll meet with a licensed provider (MD, DO, or NP) who focuses on Malassezia conditions. Before the visit, you fill out some questions and upload photos. During the visit, they'll go through your history, look at your skin, and tell you what's going on — plus what to do about it.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">Can I get a prescription?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">Yes. If your provider thinks you need Rx treatment, they'll send the prescription straight to your pharmacy. That includes antifungals, retinoids, and other meds used for Malassezia conditions.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">Is this covered by insurance?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">It depends on your plan. A lot of insurance covers virtual derm visits, but not all. Worth checking with your provider before booking. We'll give you everything you need to file a claim.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">How is my health information protected?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">Your info stays locked down. All consultations happen on a HIPAA-compliant platform, your medical data is encrypted, and we never share it with third parties. Our care platform is completely separate from the shop — your health info and your shopping cart don't mix.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">I already used the Ingredient Checker. Should I still book?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">The Checker is great for cleaning up your routine, but it can't tell you what condition you have. A provider can look at your skin, confirm what's actually going on, and prescribe things you can't buy over the counter. They're different tools for different problems.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">How much does a consultation cost?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a" data-price="faq_pricing">A Skin Assessment is $35 (one-time). Treatment Plans start at $42/mo on quarterly billing ($126 every 3 months) or $49/mo if you go monthly. Treatment + Delivery is $59/mo quarterly ($177/3 months) or $69/mo monthly. Every plan covers your consultation, prescriptions, and refills. We use Stripe for payments.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">Do you offer quarterly billing?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">Yep. Pay monthly or quarterly — quarterly saves you about 15%. That's $126 every 3 months ($42/mo) for the Treatment Plan, or $177 every 3 months ($59/mo) for Treatment + Delivery. You can switch between them whenever you want from your account.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">Can I pause instead of canceling?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">For sure. Hit pause for up to 90 days — no charges, no shipments. Your treatment plan and notes stay saved, so when you're ready to come back, everything's right where you left it. Pause or unpause anytime from your account.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">Do I need to upload photos?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">You don't have to, but it really helps your provider. You can upload up to 5 photos when you book. We strip all location and device data from them automatically, and only your provider can see them.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">How do I pick my pharmacy?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">When you're booking, just search by name or ZIP code and pick the one you want. If your provider writes a prescription, it goes straight there.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">What payment methods do you take?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">All major credit and debit cards (Visa, Mastercard, Amex, Discover), plus Apple Pay and Google Pay. Everything runs through Stripe.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('.th-faq__q').forEach(function(btn) {
    btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
      var answer = this.nextElementSibling;
      var isOpen = answer.classList.contains('open');
      document.querySelectorAll('.th-faq__a').forEach(function(a) { a.classList.remove('open'); });
      document.querySelectorAll('.th-faq__q').forEach(function(q) { q.classList.remove('active'); });
      if (!isOpen) {
        answer.classList.add('open');
        this.classList.add('active');
      }
    });
  });

  // Billing toggle — Monthly / Quarterly
  (function() {
    var toggle = document.getElementById('billingToggle');
    if (!toggle) return;
    var btns = toggle.querySelectorAll('.th-billing-toggle__btn');
    btns.forEach(function(btn) {
      btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
        var cycle = this.getAttribute('data-cycle');
        btns.forEach(function(b) { b.classList.remove('active'); });
        this.classList.add('active');
        document.querySelectorAll('.th-pricing-cards [data-billing]').forEach(function(panel) {
          panel.style.display = panel.getAttribute('data-billing') === cycle ? 'grid' : 'none';
        });
      });
    });
  })();

  // Dynamic pricing from Supabase — single source of truth
  (function() {
    var SUPABASE_URL = 'https://pbriwsgraemyqhkymneq.supabase.co';
    var SUPABASE_KEY = 'eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJzdXBhYmFzZSIsInJlZiI6InBicml3c2dyYWVteXFoa3ltbmVxIiwicm9sZSI6ImFub24iLCJpYXQiOjE3NzUwNTQxNjEsImV4cCI6MjA5MDYzMDE2MX0.AFfCsWNblX3MzjOJVRL7JefLzaLQrsc6xHSeDZuFWrI';

    fetch(SUPABASE_URL + '/rest/v1/pricing_config?select=key,value', {
      headers: { 'apikey': SUPABASE_KEY }
    })
    .then(function(r) { return r.json(); })
    .then(function(prices) {
      var p = {};
      prices.forEach(function(row) { p[row.key] = Math.round(Number(row.value)); });

      // Monthly prices
      var treatEl = document.querySelector('[data-price="treatment_monthly"]');
      if (treatEl && p.treatment_self) {
        treatEl.innerHTML = '$' + p.treatment_self + '<span style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.6;">/mo</span>';
      }

      var delivEl = document.querySelector('[data-price="treatment_delivered"]');
      if (delivEl && p.treatment_delivered) {
        delivEl.innerHTML = '$' + p.treatment_delivered + '<span style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.6;">/mo</span>';
      }

      // Assessment price (both tabs)
      var assessEls = document.querySelectorAll('[data-price="assessment_price"], [data-price="assessment_price_q"]');
      assessEls.forEach(function(el) {
        if (p.assessment_price) el.textContent = '$' + p.assessment_price;
      });

      // Quarterly prices
      if (p.treatment_self_quarterly) {
        var qMonthly = Math.round(p.treatment_self_quarterly / 3);
        var qTreatEl = document.querySelector('[data-price="treatment_quarterly_monthly"]');
        if (qTreatEl) qTreatEl.innerHTML = '$' + qMonthly + '<span style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.6;">/mo</span>';
        var qTotalEl = document.querySelector('[data-price="treatment_quarterly_total"]');
        if (qTotalEl) qTotalEl.textContent = 'Billed $' + p.treatment_self_quarterly + ' every 3 months';
      }

      if (p.treatment_delivered_quarterly) {
        var qdMonthly = Math.round(p.treatment_delivered_quarterly / 3);
        var qdTreatEl = document.querySelector('[data-price="treatment_delivered_quarterly_monthly"]');
        if (qdTreatEl) qdTreatEl.innerHTML = '$' + qdMonthly + '<span style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.6;">/mo</span>';
        var qdTotalEl = document.querySelector('[data-price="treatment_delivered_quarterly_total"]');
        if (qdTotalEl) qdTotalEl.textContent = 'Billed $' + p.treatment_delivered_quarterly + ' every 3 months';
      }

      // Update FAQ pricing text
      var faqEl = document.querySelector('[data-price="faq_pricing"]');
      if (faqEl && p.assessment_price && p.treatment_self && p.treatment_self_quarterly) {
        var qm = Math.round(p.treatment_self_quarterly / 3);
        var qdm = p.treatment_delivered_quarterly ? Math.round(p.treatment_delivered_quarterly / 3) : 59;
        faqEl.textContent = 'Skin Assessments are $' + p.assessment_price + ' (one-time diagnosis). Treatment Plans start at $' + qm + '/month when billed quarterly ($' + p.treatment_self_quarterly + ' every 3 months), or $' + p.treatment_self + '/month billed monthly. Treatment + Delivery starts at $' + qdm + '/month quarterly or $' + p.treatment_delivered + '/month billed monthly. All plans include your consultation, prescription medication, and refills. Payment is processed securely through Stripe.';
      }
    })
    .catch(function() { /* keep hardcoded defaults */ });
  })();
</script>

